	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non habeo, quae his addam nunc, quę his diebus copiose ad te scripsi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expecto nunc tuum responsum, praesertim de <placeName type="auto_name">Castalione</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fertur (non tamen certe adhuc affirmare ausim) <persName type="citizen_name">Condensem</persName>, postquam frustra se pacem hactenus sperasse et adversarios extrema tentare videt, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglos</placeName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> introducturum; in itinere etiam esse magnas ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> copias, quę illi suppetias ferant.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus det successum, ut liberentur ecclesię tandem tam gravi tyrannide!</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Quod <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l646" cert="high">Glaronenses</placeName> attinet,</foreign> wöltend min herren gern ein gwüßes mit den Stetten abreden, und ist inen sin ernst; es wil aber bi vilen nitt tönen.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Unsere botten habend gwallt ghan, mitt den anderen Stetten überzuͦsitzen und articulieren.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Üwer herren sind vil dabi gsin, da man red mitt einanderen ghalten, doch nitt wyteren befelch ghan dann allein zlosen, was man an si bring, nitt zuͦ articulieren.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">So ist das miner herren meinung keinswägs, das man nun amm <placeName type="auto_name">Brünig</placeName> lige, wie man inens ußleit; sonder habend das zuͦ bedencken fürgworffen, das wir an den anstößen auch müßtind sorg han und eben nitt mitt aller macht möchtind den <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l646" cert="high">Glarneren</placeName> zuͦ ylen.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dann wir habend bös anstöß mitt <placeName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="l2469">Underwalden</placeName>, <placeName ref="l160" cert="high">Fryburg</placeName> und <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Solloturn</placeName>; die ligend uns schier mitten imm land und vermögend nitt nüt.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Darumb wärs guͦt, das man mitt ernst drüber säß und es eigenlich berathschlagte; dann wenn es lang gat, so wirt es sin dörffen.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName> zücht sich schier gar us.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich glaub, si wärind lieber wider <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2481" cert="high">Schwaben</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich hör, man sölle nun znechst mitt vollmechtigem gwallt wider zemmen kon; das wär guͦt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribe, obsecro, si quid ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> habueris, item ex conventu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l300" cert="high">Lucernensi</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego nihildum inde habeo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribit d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3659" cert="high">Beatus Ludovicus a Mülinen</persName> ipsemet ad te.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Reliqui te omnes salutant, <persName ref="p8063" cert="high">Steigerus</persName>, <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p8012">Hallerus</persName>, <persName ref="p8389" cert="high">Hagius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4791">Vischerus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p5787">a Madiis</persName>, <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p9046">Pistorius</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4060" cert="high">Zehenderi</persName>, <persName ref="p8417" cert="high">Musculus</persName> item, socer meus et mater.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta dominos et amicos omnes, d. <persName ref="p8111" cert="high">Martyrem</persName>, <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltherum</persName>, generos denique omnes cum uxore et familia universa.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> 16. augusti 1562.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[oannes] H[allerus</persName>] tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae pastori fidelissimo, domino suo honorando et compatri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
